latestPosts.caption: not us blushing over a blush 🤭

Not every dream is loud.
Some are soft, slow, and deeply personal.

I’ve been thinking about the kind of life I want.
One that doesn’t revolve around success, money, or being seen.
But around stillness, connection, softness.
A life where I’m not chasing the next thing
but pausing to feel this one.

I’m still far off.
Because how can you not help but compare, in a world where it feels like everyone is achieving everything, all the time?

But hey a girl can dream.

#SoftLife #GentleLiving #HustleCultureDropout #SlowLiving #DreamsThatMatter
